  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"100061360\" data-ratio=\"0.5453703703703704\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=49df5ba1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FINNfEriciaG5dvxVKUibFHtBAHA8WgAO3oFK1AfEQLMibKaHn0nesC1Gbv5w72o5A6lib0ZYTyPvU6llvf1PD0Hf1UA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <blockquote style=\"display: block;font-size: 0.9em;overflow: auto;overflow-scrolling: touch;border-left: 3px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);padding-top: 10px;padding-bottom: 10px;border-left-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);margin-top: 1.2em;margin-bottom: 1.2em;padding-right: 1em;padding-left: 1em;border-left-width: 4px;color: rgb(119, 119, 119);quotes: none;\">\n   <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: start;white-space: normal;text-size-adjust: auto;margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue',\n    'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei',\n    Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(119, 119, 119);line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\">本期看点：DeepSeek V3.2 在多个数学/编程竞赛中获得金牌，Mistral 3 系列模型发布，State of AI 2025 报告发布，Claude Quickstarts：Anthropic 开源的应用开发模板集合。</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <blockquote style=\"display: block;font-size: 0.9em;overflow: auto;overflow-scrolling: touch;border-left: 3px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);padding-top: 10px;padding-bottom: 10px;border-left-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);margin-top: 1.2em;margin-bottom: 1.2em;padding-right: 1em;padding-left: 1em;border-left-width: 4px;color: rgb(119, 119, 119);quotes: none;\">\n   <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: start;white-space: normal;text-size-adjust: auto;margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue',\n    'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei',\n    Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(119, 119, 119);line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：TimLi</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"padding-top:8px;margin:0;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;padding-bottom:8px;font-size:15px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;word-wrap: break-word;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><span leaf=\"\">DeepSeek V3.2 发布正式版</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- DeepSeek 发布 V3.2 正式版，平衡推理能力与输出长度，适合日常问答和通用 Agent 任务。在公开推理类 Benchmark 测试中达到 GPT-5 水平，略低于 Gemini-3.0-Pro。同时推出 DeepSeek-V3.2-Speciale，为长思考增强版，结合 DeepSeek-Math-V2 的定理证明能力，性能媲美 Gemini-3.0-Pro。V3.2-Speciale 在 IMO 2025、CMO 2025、ICPC World Finals 2025 和 IOI 2025 中均获得金牌。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"padding:16px 20px;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.476px;display:flex;font-size:12px;border-color:rgb(62, 62, 62);box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;border-radius:6px;box-shadow:rgb(199, 201, 204) 0px 0px 0px inset;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;margin-top:12px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;align-items:center;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 0 !important;padding-right: 12px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;flex: 1 1 0%;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: space-between;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <strong style=\"font-size: 12px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);line-height: 1.75em;font-weight: bold;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\">长按识别二维码查看原文</span></strong>\n    <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;margin: 0;font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;text-align: start;white-space: normal;text-size-adjust: auto;font-size: 12px;margin-bottom: 0;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;min-height: 1em;line-height: 1.8;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);word-break: break-all;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/ohsU1xRrYu9xcVD7qu5lNw\" target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/ohsU1xRrYu9xcVD7qu5lNw</a></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;max-width: 90px;box-sizing: border-box;flex-shrink: 0;font-size: 0px;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100061352\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"164\" style=\"margin: 0 auto;max-width: 100%;margin-right: auto;margin-left: auto;box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;border-style: none;display: block;border-radius: 4px;overflow-wrap: break-word;visibility: visible;width: 90px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=820f80b6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FINNfEriciaG5dvxVKUibFHtBAHA8WgAO3oFHicNBia3CL9kCXiaYOUeLibYghXia3tGwk2ghZxnMnowNriaLypLOhvMjBzg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"padding-top:8px;margin:0;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;padding-bottom:8px;font-size:15px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;word-wrap: break-word;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><span leaf=\"\">Mistral 发布 Mistral 3 系列模型</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- Mistral 发布 Mistral 3 系列，包含 Mistral Large 3（675B 参数的 MoE 模型，推理时激活 41B）和 Ministral 3 系列（3B、8B、14B 三个密集模型）。Large 3 支持 256K token 上下文窗口，在 40+ 语言上表现优秀，支持文本和图像理解，在 LMArena 排行榜上排名开源非推理模型第 2，性能与 DeepSeek V3.1、Kimi K2 相当。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"padding:16px 20px;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.476px;display:flex;font-size:12px;border-color:rgb(62, 62, 62);box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;border-radius:6px;box-shadow:rgb(199, 201, 204) 0px 0px 0px inset;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;margin-top:12px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;align-items:center;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 0 !important;padding-right: 12px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;flex: 1 1 0%;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: space-between;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <strong style=\"font-size: 12px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);line-height: 1.75em;font-weight: bold;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\">长按识别二维码查看原文</span></strong>\n    <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;margin: 0;font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;text-align: start;white-space: normal;text-size-adjust: auto;font-size: 12px;margin-bottom: 0;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;min-height: 1em;line-height: 1.8;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);word-break: break-all;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://mistral.ai/news/mistral-3\" target=\"_blank\">https://mistral.ai/news/mistral-3</a></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;max-width: 90px;box-sizing: border-box;flex-shrink: 0;font-size: 0px;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100061350\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"148\" style=\"margin: 0 auto;max-width: 100%;margin-right: auto;margin-left: auto;box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;border-style: none;display: block;border-radius: 4px;overflow-wrap: break-word;visibility: visible;width: 90px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2b0b43a1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FINNfEriciaG5dvxVKUibFHtBAHA8WgAO3oFbbEo64RBPKqAOCoBHezQ9VZoJXQ5xicc5Fibapel8QYt6Wb82cia4N7Yg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"padding-top:8px;margin:0;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;padding-bottom:8px;font-size:15px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;word-wrap: break-word;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><span leaf=\"\">State of AI 2025：基于 100 万亿 token 的真实使用数据报告</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- A16z 与 OpenRouter 联合发布 State of AI 2025，基于超过 100 万亿 token 的真实 LLM 使用数据。主要发现：开源模型使用率增长至近 30%，其中中国模型（DeepSeek、Qwen、Kimi 等）份额从 2024 年底的 1.2% 增至 2025 年中近 30%；开源模型中角色扮演和创意交互占比超 50%，超过编程和企业工作流；编程相关查询从 11% 增至 50% 以上，Claude 处理超 60% 的编程工作负载；多步推理模型处理半数 token，工具调用和更长提示词使用增加；亚洲 AI 支出份额从 13% 翻倍至 31%，美国仍占 47% 但差距在缩小。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"padding:16px 20px;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.476px;display:flex;font-size:12px;border-color:rgb(62, 62, 62);box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;border-radius:6px;box-shadow:rgb(199, 201, 204) 0px 0px 0px inset;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;margin-top:12px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;align-items:center;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 0 !important;padding-right: 12px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;flex: 1 1 0%;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: space-between;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <strong style=\"font-size: 12px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);line-height: 1.75em;font-weight: bold;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\">长按识别二维码查看原文</span></strong>\n    <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;margin: 0;font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;text-align: start;white-space: normal;text-size-adjust: auto;font-size: 12px;margin-bottom: 0;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;min-height: 1em;line-height: 1.8;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);word-break: break-all;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://openrouter.ai/state-of-ai\" target=\"_blank\">https://openrouter.ai/state-of-ai</a></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;max-width: 90px;box-sizing: border-box;flex-shrink: 0;font-size: 0px;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100061349\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"148\" style=\"margin: 0 auto;max-width: 100%;margin-right: auto;margin-left: auto;box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;border-style: none;display: block;border-radius: 4px;overflow-wrap: break-word;visibility: visible;width: 90px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5e451bbf&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FINNfEriciaG5dvxVKUibFHtBAHA8WgAO3oF7oTMRP0IWKFa1SlXQSztoPFYTQULDEIWVIHZGesrmy5bkticUnSN0UA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"padding-top:8px;margin:0;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;padding-bottom:8px;font-size:15px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;word-wrap: break-word;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><span leaf=\"\">AI-Native 时代的软件研发新范式</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- Rainman 撰文探讨 AI-Native 时代软件研发从传统编码向“上下文工程”（Context Engineering）的转变。文章强调通过精心设计和管理 AI 模型的输入上下文，引导模型生成符合预期的输出。实践包括需求明确化、提示设计、结果评估与迭代等步骤。该方法可提高开发效率、增强代码质量，促进人机协作。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"padding:16px 20px;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.476px;display:flex;font-size:12px;border-color:rgb(62, 62, 62);box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;border-radius:6px;box-shadow:rgb(199, 201, 204) 0px 0px 0px inset;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;margin-top:12px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;align-items:center;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 0 !important;padding-right: 12px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;flex: 1 1 0%;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: space-between;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <strong style=\"font-size: 12px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);line-height: 1.75em;font-weight: bold;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\">长按识别二维码查看原文</span></strong>\n    <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;margin: 0;font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;text-align: start;white-space: normal;text-size-adjust: auto;font-size: 12px;margin-bottom: 0;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;min-height: 1em;line-height: 1.8;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);word-break: break-all;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://deusyu.app/posts/context-engineering-ai-native/\" target=\"_blank\">https://deusyu.app/posts/context-engineering-ai-native/</a></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;max-width: 90px;box-sizing: border-box;flex-shrink: 0;font-size: 0px;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><im